<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">لِلرَّاجِزِ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(وَتَقْنَعِي بِالعَرْفَجِ المُشَجَّجِ ... )</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(وَبِالثُّمَامَ وعُرامِ العَوْسَجِ ... )</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَعمَّه غَيرُه فَقَالَ:</span> عُرامُ الشَّجَرَةِ: قِشْرُهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> العُرامُ <span class="c2">(من الرَّجُلِ: الشَّرَاسَةُ)</span> ، والشِّدَّةُ، والقُوَّةُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> العُرامُ: <span class="c2">(الأَذَى)</span> ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ حُمَيْدُ بنُ ثَوْرٍ الهِلَالِيُّ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(حَمَى ظِلَّهَا شَكْسُ الخَلِيقَةِ حَائِطُ ... عَلَيْهَا عُرامُ الطَّائِفِينَ شَفِيقُ)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(عَرمَ)</span> الرَّجلُ، <span class="c2">(كَنَصَرَ وَضَرَبَ وكَرُمَ وعَلِمَ)</span> ، واقْتَصَرَ الجَوْهَرِيُّ على الأَوَّلَيْنِ <span class="c2">(عَرَامةً وعُرَامًا، بِالضَّمِّ)</span> .<span class="c5"> قَالَ وَعْلَةُ الجَرْسِيُّ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(أَلَمْ تَعْلَمُوا أَنِّي تُخَافُ عَرَامَتِي ... وأَنَّ قَنَاتِي لَا تَلِينُ عَلَى الكَسْرِ)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(فَهُوَ عَارِمٌ وعَرِمٌ)</span> ، أَي <span class="c2">(اشْتَدَّ)</span> قَالَ:<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(إنِّي امرؤٌ يَذُبُّ عَن مَحَارِمِي ... )</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(بَسْطَةُ كَفٍّ ولِسَانٍ عَارِمِ ... )</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> عَرُمَ <span class="c2">(الصَّبِيُّ عَلَيْنَا)</span> عَرَامَةً وعُرَامَ: <span class="c2">(أَشِرَ ومَرِحَ أَو بَطِرَ أَو فَسَدَ)</span> فَهُوَ عَارِمٌ وعَرِمٌ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ ابنُ الأَعْرَابِيّ:</span> العَرِم الجَاهِلُ، وَقد عَرَمَ يَعْرُم وعَرُمَ وعَرِمَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(وَيَوْمٌ عَارِمٌ)</span> : شَدِيدُ البَرْدِ،<span class="c5"> وقِيلَ:</span> <span class="c2">(نِهايةٌ فِي البَرْدِ)</span> ، وَكَذَا لَيْلٌ عَارِمٌ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(وَعَرِمَ العَظْمَ)</span> يَعْرِمُه ويَعْرُمُه عَرْمًا: <span class="c2">(نَزَع مَا عَلَيْه مِنْ لَحْمٍ كَتَعَرَّمَهُ)</span> ، وكَذَلِكَ عَرَقَه وتَعَرَّقَه.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> عَرَمَ <span class="c2">(الصَّبِيُّ أُمَّه)</span> عَرْمًا: <span class="c2">(رَضَعَها)</span> .<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> عَرَمَتِ <span class="c2">(الإِبِلُ الشَّجَرَ: نَالَتْ مِنْه)</span> نَقَلَهُ الجَوْهَرِيُّ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(و)</span> عَرَمَ <span class="c2">(فُلانًا)</span> عَرامةً: <span class="c2">(أَصَابَه بعُرامٍ)</span> أَي شَراسَةٍ:<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c2">(وعَرِمَ العَظْمُ - كفَرِح)</span> -<span class="c5"> عَرَمًا:</span> <span class="c2">(فَتِر)</span> هَكَذا فِي النُّسَخ،<span class="c5"> والصَّواب:</span> قَتِرَ.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>